@startuml Autotext
' Autotext — abbreviation expansion at the firmware level.
' Watch typed sequences, match against a trigger table, replace with expansions.
' 2-state SM: IDLE (no partial match) vs ACCUMULATING (partial match in progress).
' See docs/plans/2026-05-24-autotext-design.md in the firmware repo for full design.

state idle
state accumulating

[*] -> idle

idle --> accumulating : on_first_match_char
idle --> idle         : on_non_match_char

accumulating --> accumulating : on_extend_match
accumulating --> idle         : on_full_match
accumulating --> idle         : on_break_match

/'! $CONFIG : toml
SmRunnerSettings.transpilerId = "C99"
'/
@enduml
